# syslog or auditd with these two options rich rules can be implemented as to trace accepted or rejected connections

# logging syntax 
log [prefix="<PREFIX TEXT>"] [level=<LOGLEVEL>] [limit value="<RATE/DURATION>"]

# LOGLEVEL can be:
emerg
alert
crit
error
warning
notice
info
debug

# DURATION can be:
s
m
h




